definitions.definition: Just sufficient to return to base (or, alternatively, to divert to an alternative airfield). ( also written Bingo or BINGO )
definitions.label_groups: US , aviation slang , chiefly military , primarily of fuel

main_definition: ( US , aviation slang , chiefly military , primarily of fuel ) Just sufficient to return to base (or, alternatively, to divert to an alternative airfield). ( also written Bingo or BINGO )
